tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Population_Health_Data (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR,
  diagnosis VARCHAR,
  treatment VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE population_data (
  patient_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  location VARCHAR(50),
  health_condition VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    address VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE medical_records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
    date_of_visit DATE,
    doctor_name VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE healthcare_providers (
    provider_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_name VARCHAR(50),
    specialty VARCHAR(50),
    location VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE insurance_plans (
    plan_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    plan_name VARCHAR(50),
    coverage_details VARCHAR(200)
)

CREATE TABLE population_demographics (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR,
  location VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE health_conditions (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID,
  condition VARCHAR,
  diagnosis_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE healthcare_providers (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR,
  specialty VARCHAR,
  location VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE medical_records (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID,
  provider_id UUID,
  record_date DATE,
  diagnosis VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE predictive_models (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name VARCHAR,
  model_type VARCHAR,
  accuracy FLOAT
)
